In this problem, Observer design pattern can be used as when a Ball is balled, The score sheet of Batsman on the strike and the bowler 
and overall innigs score board needs to be updated.
Every player maintains the bowling and Batting score sheet. 

Clases that can be created are Match which has Team a, Team B, Innings array. Then Team has List of Players. 
Player class which has bowling and Batting score sheet.
Bowling sheet has attrbutes like number of overs, maiden number, economy, wickets
Batting sheet has runs, balls played, strike rate number of 4s and no. of 6s
There will be MathcType enum like t20, oneday and the number of overs will be mentioned there.
There will Over calls which has List of Balls. On every ball there can be 0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 6 runs.
And according the innning, bowler player and bastmans players sheet will be updated using observer pattern.

